Date:   Sat May 15 19:26:51 2010 +0200

    Documentation: Use postfix notation for all method calls.
    
    Replase "foo $A" with "$A->foo". The prefix method looks like a
    function and invites the use to write "foo($A)" which works
    inconsistently.

